casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Sylvester DAVIS III, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159563
COA: 347464 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 14, 2019 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
